            <td>-wide¹</td>
            <td colspan="2">— smaller vertical space</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

**Exclusions:**

1. Suffixes `-tall` and `-wide` can't be used together with `.space-auto`.  
    Suffixes `-tall` and `-wide` doesn't exist for `-zero` and `-nano` spacings.

